    <item>
      <title>初请失业金人数降至接近历史低位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-21/jobless-claims-ease-to-near-historically-low-levels-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据劳工部周四公布的数据，截至 3 月 16 日当周，美国首次申请失业救济人数减少 2,000 人，至 210,000 人。彭博社经济学家调查的预测中位数为 213,000。迈克·麦基报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-21/jobless-claims-ease-to-near-historically-low-levels-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 13:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
